com.salesforce.omakase.broadcast.annotation

Annotation Type Subscribable


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface Subscribable
    Indicates that a Syntax unit can be subscribed to within a Plugin.

    Note that just because a Syntax unit can be subscribed to doesn't mean that it will necessarily be broadcasted. For more information see the readme file regarding refinement.
